snippet.title: TINY LANDS - Announcement trailer.
snippet.description:
Tiny Lands is a relaxing game where you have to find the differences in 3D and experience a beautiful environment. 

Available on Steam
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1354910/Tiny_Lands/

Nintendo Switch:
https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/tiny-lands-switch/

Many thanks to the great music composer for the game, we are sure you will love BigRicePiano awesome music.
https://www.youtube.com/user/BigRiceRecords



This video music credits: Pianowild by VABsounds https://freesound.org/people/VABsounds/ 
#Findthedifferences #spot #find #SpotTheDifference #Gamedev #indiegames #puzzle #3D #puzzlegames #odd #chill #relaxingame #lofi
